♪Hairpins carved
with endless sighs and regrets♪

278
00:16:57,476 --> 00:17:02,148
♪Fate laid bare my deepest thoughts♪

279
00:17:02,692 --> 00:17:04,452
♪Like vows, like remorse, like love♪

280
00:17:04,772 --> 00:17:08,388
♪Loving, hurting,
